{"tid":1851394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天津患者check足4次，先確定陽性","createTime":"2020-01-30T04:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T04:35:58.000Z","uid":132380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c139281bc406320512c31952be9308a8a4ddf2d2","tid":1851394,"uid":132380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"据天津市疾控中心，天津第28例患者，1月19日出现发热，1月25日两次核酸检测阴性，1月27日再次发热，1月28日核酸检测阴性，1月30日第四次检测为阳性。后经市专家组确诊为普通型病例，目前生命体征平稳。 （人民日报）"},{"pid":"45b0a3bdc67a292ea1e1fe92fc28106a4e68e665","tid":1851394,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n而家已經係獨立最佳時機，你，仲等緊啲咩<br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：種族清洗 香港人，仲唔反佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1851323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1851323</a>"},{"pid":"1c4064d69d9c210f4ba1054cb7c10b362c725a10","tid":1851394,"uid":75311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"港共: 唔check咪無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8fdc622825f5ed0c3eafb2329145bed384b394f","tid":1851394,"uid":256142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:29:30.000Z","msg":"彈出又彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04fddfa1f344f8934a5e2bf01443d8eee59706bb","tid":1851394,"uid":277702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:35:58.000Z","msg":"一路都覺得係啲試劑有問題..."}]}